==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: One arrow, two eagles.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī jìan shūang dīao

===Idiom===
[[一]][[箭]][[双]][[雕]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# {{idiom}} [[kill two birds with one stone]]; do one task and finish two or more goals.

===Alternate forms===
